- `drainToolDurability` mirrors `spendToolStamina` exactly: read tool config, delegate to store. The store method is where the actual math and state mutation live.
- `maxDurability === 0` is the "exempt" sentinel — almanac and seed-pouch have no wear. Same pattern as `staminaCost === 0` in `spendToolStamina`.
- Lazy init: absence from `toolDurabilities` map = full durability. First drain initializes from `maxDurability`, avoiding any startup reset cost.
